{"tid":944176,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「天安門沒死一個人」 國務院前發言人袁木離世　終年90歲","createTime":"2018-12-17T03:10:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-17T10:55:29.000Z","uid":39464,"like":57,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"a506e810c6e7a9694f23e5facd5169b037bcdf75","tid":944176,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T03:10:45.000Z","msg":"1989年「六四屠城」後指天安門沒一個人死亡的國務院前發言人袁木，本月13日在北京去世，終年90歲。據悉，有關方面已成立袁木同志治喪工作小組，上海澎湃新聞網已證實有關袁木去世的消息。<br />\n<br />\n袁木出生於1928年1月1日，江蘇省興化市昭陽鎮人，記者出身，曾任國務院研究室主任、國務院發言人、第八屆全國政協常委。六四事件期間多次跟學生對話並代表國務院發佈消息。<br />\n<br />\n袁木1989年在6月6日發佈六四事件一些不完全的暫時統計數字:「死亡情況，軍隊和地方加在一起的初步統計數字是近三百人，其中包括部隊的戰士，包括罪有應得的歹徒，也包括誤傷的群眾，當中包括23名是北京各個大學的學生。」6月17日，袁木在接受美國電視記者採訪時表示，戒嚴部隊在天安門廣場執行清場任務的過程中「沒有死一個人，沒有軋傷一個人。」<br />\n<br />\n他的妻子在多年之後說這些數字是李鵬當年向袁木轉達中央政治局常委的決定，責任不在她的丈夫。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20181217/59038542\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181217%2F59038542&d=t%2F78%2BODoCXm3BL3z0AU5BVKzBYqMCiHg3GgvTcrvEuQ%3D&h=f4c07e98\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181217%2F59038542&h=f27544c4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20181217/59038542</a>"},{"pid":"8b7692e43029132481cae211cd9726747cf37f2c","tid":944176,"uid":37733,"like":2,"dislike":47,"score":-45,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T03:11:52.000Z","msg":"2018又死一個偉人"},{"pid":"86395a7ab14c4721e0e03efc5e5c8f439aac8051","tid":944176,"uid":100016,"like":3,"dislike":37,"score":-34,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T03:12:52.000Z","msg":"可以壽終正寢, 證明佢講既係事實, 報應撚收皮"},{"pid":"ce9acf5f6232ac3eb3b41d35cbbcc289d68defd5","tid":944176,"uid":28765,"like":79,"dislike":0,"score":79,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T03:12:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://lh5.ggpht.com/_S1q9CdzI59Q/TAqVgZaBAAI/AAAAAAAAAaw/yro7C2yps_A/s0/%E8%A2%81%E6%9C%A8%E5%A5%BD%E8%AA%A0%E5%AF%A6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Flh5.ggpht.com%2F_S1q9CdzI59Q%2FTAqVgZaBAAI%2FAAAAAAAAAaw%2Fyro7C2yps_A%2Fs0%2F%25E8%25A2%2581%25E6%259C%25A8%25E5%25A5%25BD%25E8%25AA%25A0%25E5%25AF%25A6.jpg&h=0d3c0a33&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"19dafedd8112e0391a19ae7aa471e5102aaf6e75","tid":944176,"uid":136666,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T03:13:16.000Z","msg":"恭喜落地獄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b84758f645371c6934ed9361275991f9f93b223f","tid":944176,"uid":177590,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T03:13:21.000Z","msg":"袁木好誠實"},{"pid":"301b5c55f65952e1d20026f56a7d5642199adcef","tid":944176,"uid":17859,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T03:13:36.000Z","msg":"袁木之女<br />\n<br />\n大名鼎鼎的前國務院反美名嘴袁木，也把女兒送到美國辦上了綠卡，不辦不放心啊！老了也有個「靠」嘛！而極具諷刺意味的是，袁木恰是6&bull;4血案的前台代表ZF放言的首席人物，美國不報復他，反而歡迎他到老奔來這個自由大陸，太諷刺了！<br />\n1989年「六四事件」後，袁木在6日的官方新聞發布會稱，「只死了23位學生」，他的名字從那時起，廣為世人所知<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.epochtimes.com.tw/n222753/反美是工作-留美是生活%E3%80%82%E3%80%82%E3%80%82看看移民美國的中共反美鬥士們.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.epochtimes.com.tw%2Fn222753%2F%E5%8F%8D%E7%BE%8E%E6%98%AF%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C-%E7%95%99%E7%BE%8E%E6%98%AF%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB%25E3%2580%2582%25E3%2580%2582%25E3%2580%2582%E7%9C%8B%E7%9C%8B%E7%A7%BB%E6%B0%91%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%AD%E5%85%B1%E5%8F%8D%E7%BE%8E%E9%AC%A5%E5%A3%AB%E5%80%91.html&d=t%2F78%2BODoCXm3BL3z0AU5BVKzBYqMCiHg3GgvTcrvEuQ%3D&h=878aebec\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.epochtimes.com.tw/n222753/反美是工作-留美是生活%E3%80%82%E3%80%82%E3%80%82看看移民美國的中共反美鬥士們.html</a>"},{"pid":"ca2985da3be1c58652fc992cf37ebc03288ec6b8","tid":944176,"uid":60281,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T03:13:59.000Z","msg":"又走一件<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89d4a07f5ddfbc4d